OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1775070658
OL,3,CManxman Nathan Harrison to return to
OL,4,CIsle of Man TT 'fully fit' after injury
OL,6,FAfter winning both the Junior and
OL,7,FSenior races at the Manx Grand Prix as
OL,8,Fa 21-year-old in 2019, the local rider
OL,9,Fhas established himself on the
OL,10,FMountain Course, delivering
OL,11,Fincreasingly strong performances each
OL,12,Ftime he has competed at the event.
OL,14,FHis first TT campaign in 2022
OL,15,Fconcluded on a high note, with a tenth-
OL,16,Fplace finish in the Senior TT - an
OL,17,Fachievement that underlined his
OL,18,Fpotential around the 37.73-mile course.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1775070658
OL,3,CManxman Nathan Harrison to return to
OL,4,CIsle of Man TT 'fully fit' after injury
OL,6,FHe then joined Honda Racing, providing
OL,7,Fa dream opportunity as he lined up as
OL,8,Fteam-mate to 23-time TT winner John
OL,9,FMcGuinness in both 2023 and 2024, with
OL,10,Ffellow race winner Dean Harrison also
OL,11,Fjoining the team in 2024.
OL,13,FHowever, injuries sustained at the
OL,14,FNorth West 200 ruled Harrison out of
OL,15,Fthe 2023 TT and he was forced to wait
OL,16,Funtil the following year to line up on
OL,17,FGlencrutchery Road as a factory Honda
OL,18,Frider.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1775070658
OL,3,CManxman Nathan Harrison to return to
OL,4,CIsle of Man TT 'fully fit' after injury
OL,6,FDespite retiring from his opening two
OL,7,Fraces, the Senior TT again provided a
OL,8,Fhighlight as he improved both his
OL,9,Fresult and lap speed, finishing
OL,10,Fseventh with a fastest lap of
OL,11,F129.156mph.
OL,13,FHarrison then formed his own team for
OL,14,F2025 ` H&H Motorcycles ` continuing to
OL,15,Freceive support from Honda UK. With a
OL,16,Fclear run at the event, he emerged as
OL,17,Fone of the standout performers of race
OL,18,Fweek.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1775070658
OL,3,CManxman Nathan Harrison to return to
OL,4,CIsle of Man TT 'fully fit' after injury
OL,6,FThe Manxman then took a fourth-place
OL,7,Ffinish in the RST Superbike TT,
OL,8,Frecording his fastest lap of the TT
OL,9,FCourse to date at 131.270mph.
OL,11,FSpeaking about his return to the event
OL,12,Fin 2026, Harrison said he is eager to
OL,13,Fcontinue the progress made last year.
OL,15,FNathan Harrison said: "I was really
OL,16,Fpleased with how last year went.
OL,17,FGetting that fourth place in the
OL,18,FSuperbike TT and putting in a 131mph
OL,19,Flap showed what we can do.
OL,26,@wD@WOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1775070658
OL,3,CManxman Nathan Harrison to return to
OL,4,CIsle of Man TT 'fully fit' after injury
OL,6,F"For 2026, I want to just concentrate
OL,7,Fon myself and keep improving.
OL,9,F"It's what I've done all my career,
OL,10,Fslowly getting quicker and quicker.
OL,11,FHopefully I can add a mile an hour or
OL,12,Ftwo this year and see where we end up."
OL,14,F"Running our own team with H&H
OL,15,FMotorcycles, headed by my dad Dean has
OL,16,Fworked really well. I couldn't do it
OL,17,Fwithout him and the continued support
OL,18,Ffrom Honda UK," he added.
OL,26,@tD@gO]vD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1775070658
OL,3,CManxman Nathan Harrison to return to
OL,4,CIsle of Man TT 'fully fit' after injury
OL,6,F"We've got a strong package again. I'd
OL,7,Flove a podium. That's what I dream
OL,8,Fabout every day when I get up and
OL,9,Ftrain. Everything I'm doing is towards
OL,10,Fthat, so if I could do it, that would
OL,11,Fbe amazing."
OL,13,FHarrison, from Douglas, will again
OL,14,Fcompete on Honda machinery, lining up
OL,15,Fon a Honda CBR1000RR Fireblade in the
OL,16,FRST Superbike TT, both RL360
OL,17,FSuperstock TT races and the Milwaukee
OL,18,FSenior TT.
OL,26,@sD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
